###############################################################################

1. Python 2.7.x or 3.x is required to run aloft. 
To check your python version:
	$ python --version

To download the latest version of Python, visit www.python.org

2. Download the ALoFT software and data package
        $ Download the master.zip file form this repo
        $ gunzip aloft-master
        $ Download the input data package from http://archive.gersteinlab.org/aloft_data/data.tar.gz
	$ wget http://archive.gersteinlab.org/aloft_data/data.tar.gz
	$ tar -zxvf data.tar.gz 

3. Install VAT Dependency
      cd /path/to/aloft_directory
      python install.py

4. Run ALoFT
To see the help screen:
	$ ./aloft -h

For more complete information on running ALoFT, see QUICKSTART or README.
